Magic the Gathering: Life & Poison counters for Android.

Features:

- life & poison counters
- 1, 2, 3, or 4 players
- dice rolling
- history of last changes
- colors to identify players
- low battery consumption
- open source
- free (really!)
    - no restrictions
    - no ads

Please, feel free to send us feedback:

droid.in.the.sky@gmail.com

The source code is available in GitHub:

https://github.com/droid-in-the-sky/mtg-life

keywords: magic, mtg, life, poison, counter, dice
